Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:15.32,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance between the Emilia and \NCrusch camps, on equal terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:25.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For this purpose, I'll provide \Nthe time and location of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,the White Whale's next appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:30.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one card I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.39,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch's Cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're on the move and after Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:11.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Roswaal-sama feared that \Nmight happen, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:13.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stop them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have the fighting strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:18.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to start negotiating\Nnow to pull some together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:21.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.96,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,The White Whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.60,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my indiscretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.02,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I still have much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:48.48,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,And? It is rather sudden that you \Nwould bring up the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When we began this negotiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:57.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I mentioned the magic stones found in \NRoswaal's domain, in Elior Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If sharing the mining rights is insufficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:03.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to offer something additional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:07.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-san, I'm certain that my \Ninformation will aid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in your plan to subjugate the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.79,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask one thing, Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.51,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,What gave you that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:19.86,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,That remark was not one you might \Npass off as a baseless accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For these past few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some things have bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,First, the increase in traffic \Nto and from your mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's been just a bit excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:33.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, in the capital, I heard you've been \Npurchasing weapons and armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:34.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.27,Default - flashback,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,If Crusch-sama's goal should be attained,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.49,Default - flashback,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it would suit your\Ndesires, Wilhelm-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You appeared to be planning something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can't prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:49.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I only made the connection
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I know the White Whale \Nwill soon be appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.88,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I have another question, Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:59.76,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,On what grounds do you know\Nthat the White Whale will appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.09,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:08.89,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The moment before that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you'd call a metia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:19.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It tells me when and where the \NWhite Whale will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.24,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I find this a bit hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.96,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But I see that you are not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:31.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that, but are you sure \Nyou want to believe me so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.18,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Lies will get you {\i1}nyo{\i0}where with Crusch-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.20,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,She has the divine protection of wind-reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:42.59,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,When a person lies, a telling \Nwind blows around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.84,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.58,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You did not have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll agree to an alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for my information \Non the White Whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.27,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting ahead\Nof yourself, Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.19,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I agree to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether I believe\Nyou are separate matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.34,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,My decision will determine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the outcome of the royal selection, \Nif not the kingdom's very future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.67,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be made lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:11.68,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I listen in on this li'l chat, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.82,Default,Russel,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.84,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Anastasia Hoshin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.19,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Russell Fellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.33,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, y'all asked us to\Ncome, and here you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:24.03,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,startin' without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hardly fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.05,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Let us in on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.89,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Natsuki Subaru who \Nasked you to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:35.00,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be exact, it was this \Ngal he keeps with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.90,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,I only heard the gist,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.90,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're really plannin' to subjugate \Nthe White Whale, I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.53,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,For us business folk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:45.53,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,whether the White Whale's around \Nis a life-or-death matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.86,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, our mercenary team will help y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.43,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to the White Whale, \NI'm interested
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.28,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,in the concession that Natsuki-dono
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,proposed of mining rights to the magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.35,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,If the alliance is formed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.78,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,magic stones from pristine veins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be distributed to the capital \Nthrough Crusch-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.54,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,As the merchant guild's representative, \NI cannot let the offer go unheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:10.59,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru called you, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What I offer in return for the alliance is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,a share in the magic stone mining rights
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:20.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and information on when and where \Nthe White Whale will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the fuel needed \Nto subjugate the mabeast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's terrorized the world for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:32.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If what I say makes no sense \Nto you, forget I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But if your goal and my wish align,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,then let's defeat the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on a hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.26,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I still have several questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.81,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,but it was brilliant of you\Nto expose my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.63,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I have questions, as well as doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.34,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Many things you say are unclear to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.99,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,so I have difficulty agreeing immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:06.53,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.32,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall choose to trust your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.54,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,and the spirit that led you \Nto create this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.01,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,Then the deal is struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.42,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,There were a few touch-and-go moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.92,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad it worked out, Natsuki-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.37,Default,Russell,0000,0000,0000,,I trust the promise we made prior \Nto the negotiation still stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you were a big help, Russell-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Once the subjugation is complete, \NI'll give you the metia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.04,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,So you did lay some groundwork \Nbefore coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.47,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,And you were waiting outside the \Ndoor for your moment to enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:42.20,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,But it was up to us when we interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:45.71,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as far as negotiations go, \NI guess that just passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were never gonna enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.32,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,When negotiatin', there's always \Na time to make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:56.93,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as you're gettin' ready for \Nthe subjugation and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.37,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,don't forget to patronize the Hoshin Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:04.65,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You paved the way before negotiations began?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.92,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You are surprisingly shrewd, Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My preparation and review\Npaid off, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I couldn't be more relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.34,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's plain to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:21.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to save face for staying \Nin the capital. Right, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.19,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are truly wonderful, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.48,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.11,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:31.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.64,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I offer you gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.95,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,equal to that which I offer to my \Nlady, Duchess Crusch Karsten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er, that's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.48,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,As perceptive as you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.37,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure you're aware, but if \NI may introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.21,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,My family name is Astrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:52.97,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I took the previous Master Swordsman, \NTheresia van Astrea, as my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.72,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,giving me the honor of the \Nbloodline's lowest seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.88,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,That is who I, Wilhelm van Astrea, am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.06,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for so kindly\Ngranting this old man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.99,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,the opportunity to slay the loathsome \Nmabeast that took my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure! Of course I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I figured Crusch-san would accept \Nmy offer, keeping that in mind—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.28,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.99,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,The wind of untruth is blowing from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You bought all the dragon-drawn \Ncarriages for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,so that's why I had trouble getting \None back to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.39,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is working through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.83,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,They have {\i1}nyo{\i0} choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the White Whale will \Nappear tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,in the area around Flügel's Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:55.82,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,So, given the travel time, \Nwe'll just barely make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.69,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, can't you see it in {\i1}\Nnyall{\i0} their faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.14,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nyot{\i0} a single one is preparing unwillingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.44,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to be rid of the White Whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:11.12,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,especially Old Man Wil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,He said it took his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.02,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.97,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,He's been chasing after the \NWhite Whale all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:25.56,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since it killed the previous \NMaster Swordsman, his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The previous Master Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.21,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.13,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,so you should stop worrying and get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.48,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,There's {\i1}nyo{\i0}thing you can do to help
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with supply distribution\Nor organization, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't have to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to pick whichever one I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.08,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,What is it {\i1}nyow{\i0}? You don't like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're letting me borrow one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't tell anything about their quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:08.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like a veteran who's studied \Nnothing but ground dragons for decades...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that one from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.30,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:31.19,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,This ground dragon is a type \Nknown for extreme pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's love at first sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.29,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.98,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,But don't say, "Love at first sight."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making Rem-chan pout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.64,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be nice to it! I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.71,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,My lady was tellin' me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.95,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the star of this\Nlittle show, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.57,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ho
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That logo... And a Kararagi accent \Nfrom a demihuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're with Anastasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.38,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,What, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.37,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ricardo, head of her mercenary team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.58,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too, li'l lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down! Also, you're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll snap my neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.54,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! My lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:28.56,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,So that is the pride of Anastasia and \Nthe Hoshins, the Iron Fang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.08,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I see. They all look quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.23,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you rest well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly died a second ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so I guess you're also fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.47,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You think I am capable
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of sitting in a chair, waiting for good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.10,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more surprised that you are participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.50,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I can't fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:56.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think this human will be pretty \Nuseful against the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.09,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I must ask... On what grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not all that happy about it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:05.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I seem to be the type of \Nguy who attracts mabeasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.70,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:13.81,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, Subaru-kun has \Npreviously saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, on my borrowed ground dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:19.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run around under White Whale's \Nnose and draw its attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,while you guys launch an all-out attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the tactic I'd recommend, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.13,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Under the White Whale's... nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:33.08,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Shockingly, I sense no lies in that statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.40,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:39.65,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I would doubt my divine protection as \Noften as I have in the past half day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.47,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:53.22,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama, we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.30,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,Is this boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.74,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.39,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:02.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.19,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, our wish may come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.82,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,We could not be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.78,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:21.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It seems all of them have a history \Nwith the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:25.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, they're like Wilhelm-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:29.01,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, many are men who have \Nretired from the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:34.16,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,They have joined our subjugation \Nforce at Wilhelm's invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.36,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Their morale and experience
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.56,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,is comparable to those of the \Ncapital's active knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.40,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.23,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.14,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Four hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.78,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Since the White Whale, \Ncreated by the Jealous Witch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made the world its hunting ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.95,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,trampling the weak and dominating \Nthe land as if it were its owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.87,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,four hundred years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.78,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Countless lives have been lost in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.84,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Given its fog's unscrupulous nature, as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.80,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,the number of graves we cannot even \Ninscribe with names will only rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.93,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But those days of sitting idle end today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.10,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Today, those of us here will end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.44,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,We shall strike down the White Whale, \Nand stop further tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:26.34,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,We shall give the sorrow, which fell \Nshort of true sorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a chance to shed overdue tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.61,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,We move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:35.61,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination is Flügel's Tree, \Non the Lifaus Highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:39.26,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we shall slay the White \NWhale with our own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:51.17,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mimi! Glad to know ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.55,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Hetaro. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, not that I doubted it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the second-in-command, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.94,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.78,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I totally can't remember at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:12.56,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on, Sister,\Nyou have to sit up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.56,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Totally can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it...\NJust talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you two are brother and sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.04,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my big sister and I will do our—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.51,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,When Mimi and Hetaro are together, \Nwe're the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.03,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,And the captain's also here, \Nso we're the super strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:31.40,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, my sister and the\Ncaptain tend to be hasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:30.86,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Strongest! Strongest! Super strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.26,Default,Hetaro,0000,0000,0000,,so I usually give the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.22,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, bro? Ya look awful gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A captain shouldn't make trouble for his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.77,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a nice ground dragon ya got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed this one because \Nit seemed to like me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones you guys ride look kinda different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.91,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,They're called rigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.87,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,But ya don't see 'em too often in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.48,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,They ain't as strong as ground dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're much more agile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:06.33,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to a brawl against the Whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.16,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,that's where they really\Nshine, so watch close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:14.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you have had ground \Ndragons pull the cargo, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.01,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta manage our luggage on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.97,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,If ya think the White Whale's our only enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.14,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,you'll get the rug pulled out from under ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:28.73,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no guarantee we won't run into \Nthieves on the road, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:32.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone's got the guts to take on \Na fully armed group like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,they wouldn't settle for being thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.99,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:47.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Ricardo-sama is trying \Nto ease everyone's nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.21,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd prepared myself for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:58.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell the hero inside to awaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but it really isn't as easy as it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You sound happy, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:28.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like people have carved \Ntheir names into the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't on some field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just bad manners...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, get me a chisel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Even you should know that will \Nget you in trouble, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.94,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,With me, for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.97,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,So the White Whale is coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I am opposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using the witch's scent to draw \Nthe White Whale here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.00,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If it gives us even a slightly better \Nchance of winning, it's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For a guy who lacks in every way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:02.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can only compensate with this method.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.69,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You are wonderful, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:13.46,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That metia will tell you when \Nthe White Whale is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:17.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I set it to make noise when it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:18.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, without this—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.38,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are ya saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:28.99,Default,Suabru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If it's a lie, then how am I gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.99,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You're speaking in something \Nlike the Kararagi dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't suit you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:34.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! I mean, there's no \Nway I could be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even Crusch-san said—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.61,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I can always tell when you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:46.03,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I also know that you cannot \Ntell me why you do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,So there is no need to convince me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or wrap everything in lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:55.11,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,or try to take the blame\Non yourself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:20:01.45,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have complete \Nfaith in you, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:11.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Man! Looking up at this huge tree \Nreally fires you up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.41,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't look at it for a\Nlong time, I won't relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to look down for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.73,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:29.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I should say "thank you" instead \Nof "sorry" right now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:34.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:39.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I am far more grateful \Nto you, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.93,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,So we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Wilhelm-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a bit of the story from Felis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:02.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That you've been seeking revenge on the \NWhale ever since it took your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.04,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:09.53,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,It was all time idly spent in \Nan old man's delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.12,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You truly love your wife, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.62,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I love my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.69,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,More than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter how much time passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.76,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,My wife was a woman who \Nloved to look at flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.41,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,She never wished to wield a sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.72,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,but the sword loved her more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.52,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,With no choice but to live for the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:40.19,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,my wife accepted her fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.99,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,When I married her, I took it from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:45.40,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,forcing her to abandon the title \Nof "Master Swordsman."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:50.00,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,But the sword would not allow her to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:55.04,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-dono, I thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:59.25,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,In this battle, I can find answers \Nin my own sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:04.50,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps I shall finally be \Nable to visit my wife's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:08.18,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I can go and see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:17.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together to beat the \Nhell out of that damn whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:19.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help with everything I have, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:37.71,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Only a short time remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:02.81,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Troops, be on guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:13.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:25.02,Default - italics,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:27.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:03.79,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Troops—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:05.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let him have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.05,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Al Huma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:26.79,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Troops! Follow those two fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.86,0:24:35.98,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Against the {\c&H4D8A50&}White {\c&HFFFFFF&}Whale
